<figureCitation id="92C42A4118761372A91C5CD4FD8F1A8F" box="[526,624,1729,1752]" captionStart="FIGURES 1 – 8" captionStartId="1.[151,258,1859,1881]" captionTargetBox="[187,1380,198,1818]" captionTargetId="figure@1.[187,1381,191,1832]" captionTargetPageId="1" captionText="FIGURES 1 – 8. Polia ssp. adults. 1. P. hofer sp. n., male, holotype, China, N. Sichuan (GBG / ZSM); 2. P. h o f e r sp. n., male, paratype, China, N. Sichuan (GBG / ZSM); 3. P. h o f e r sp. n., female, paratype, China, N. Sichuan (OPB); 4. P. h o f e r sp. n., female, paratype, China, N. Sichuan (GBG / ZSM); 5. P. c o s t ir u f a, male, China, W. Sichuan, Batang (AFM); 6. P. c o s t ir u f a, male, China, W. Sichuan, Batang (OPB); 7. P. c o s ti r u f a, female, holotype, China Batang [Tibet], W. Sichuan (ZFMK); 8. P. costirufa, female, China, W. Sichuan, Litang (AFM)." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/258180/files/figure.png" pageId="0" pageNumber="577">
